AdHoc Au ditors, as delegates of Serbia, are the largest international network with 10,000 auditors in 110 countries around the world. Slovenia is the only one from the former Yugoslavia interested to public accounting act.

New Slovensko-srpske aukistiki associjacija was founded

In Zagreb in May 13th was founded new international association of Auhorised auditor presided by danjournalist M.Bubin with the core mission to achieve independence of auditors, to create the first ever social importance of auditors and audited obiects, to reduce and remove conflicts of interest, prevent and identify unlawful acts during audited procedures. New Slovenophoenic-austrian association shall have identical areas of convenence and at Republic of Serbia shall have as president dr. Alecovic.

Tax Expert`s Association in Belgrade has been founded

it creates network and basic conditions for the development of human resources, professional associations, institutions and RK working in the relations with the tax system, as well as all participants in the process of introducing sustainable changes aimed at increasing the effectiveness of the tax and customs authorities.
